Seadrill Sought to Acquire Aker Drilling’s Two Rigs, DN Reports

-- B y   M a r i a n n e   S t i g s e t
-- 
2011-02-26T09:41:01Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-26/seadrill-sought-to-acquire-aker-drilling-s-two-rigs-dn-reports.html
  Seadrill Ltd . sought to acquire Aker
Drilling ASA’s two rigs, Dagens Naeringsliv reported, citing
Aker ASA’s Chief Executive Officer Oeyvind Eriksen.  Eriksen said that while Aker was open to a merger, it would
not sell the rigs and chose to proceed with the refinancing and
listing of Aker Drilling, the Oslo-based newspaper reported.   Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Marianne Stigset at 
 mstigset@bloomberg.net  